  "title": "Construction Manager (HQ Tenders - MRT & Tunnel)/ Upto $13K+VB/ 5 days/ Paya lebar",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Up to $13,000 Basic + bonus!</strong></li><li><strong>Participate in HQ tendering on new MRT & Tunnel projects.</strong></li><li><strong>Permanent position/ 5 work days/ HQ/ Paya lebar area.</strong></li><li><strong>Our client, a reputable and leading MNC, A1 main contractor. </strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Part of the tender team participates in tendering civil and infrastructure projects. </li><li>Involving in preliminary stage, design & tender stage, construction stage to ensure delivery of the project.</li><li>Preparation of technical specifications and submissions of civil engineering work.</li><li>Involving in the feasibility study and construction planning, and ensuring delivery of services accordingly to client’s requirements.</li><li>Facilitate tender submission including coordinating with tender team, internal and external stakeholders, consultants, authorities on project requirements.</li><li>Overseeing the construction activities, planning, implementation, and monitoring work schedules in accordance to the master and detailed work programme.</li><li>Coordinate all related construction matters with subcontractor/consultant/client.</li><li>Liaise with consultants for technical issues and coordinate with subcontractors on the site activities.</li><li>Prepare report and method statement.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Civil Engineering and/or relevant field</li><li>Having experience in infrastructure projects or underground work</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information:</strong><br /><strong>To apply please click on the APPLY NOW button or email your resume to search84@searchindex.com.sg with the following details:</strong></p><ul><li>Reason for leaving each past & current employment</li><li>Salary drawn for each past & current employment</li><li>Expected Salary</li><li>Earliest availability date</li></ul><p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p><p>Lionel Cheow<br />EA License | 14C7092<br />EA Registration Number | R1105005</p>",
